issue.title: React integration.
issue.body: Want to implement React into the dashboard for gitStarted.

issue.title: Organize the code into object.
issue.body:
We have a lot of code that is just Data.

We really should have an object of each of the data points that we would want.

An example would be have an object for: index.html file.  Where we can pass in parameters and it returns a string, etc.

This removes it all from the controller/action files and makes it much cleaner and compartmentalized.
